query:
INSERT INTO refresh_tokens (id, user_id, jit, family, expires_at, created_at)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                ON CONFLICT (family) DO UPDATE
                SET jit = EXCLUDED.jit,
                    expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
                    created_at = EXCLUDED.created_at;
